### Configure Angular for Source Map Generation

Source: https://github.com/posthog/posthog.com/blob/master/contents/docs/error-tracking/upload-source-maps/angular.mdx

This JSON configuration snippet modifies your angular.json file to enable the generation of source maps for scripts, styles, and vendor files. Ensure this is set for production builds to capture necessary debugging information.

```json
